{"tid":1833301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[做狗做到無尊嚴] 點睇班狗完全當上司講嘢係廢嗡","createTime":"2020-01-21T21:05:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T10:48:36.000Z","uid":5416,"like":411,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":96,"replies":[{"pid":"b636425f0cd1c4e4715518a2a47ff0d66f64f7fe","tid":1833301,"uid":5416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T21:05:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/dbs.dbc/videos/125789368601775/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdbs.dbc%2Fvideos%2F125789368601775%2F&d=fvWYig%2FFXUG8IHhaG2JvmF8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=fe19f889\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/dbs.dbc/videos/125789368601775/</a><br />\n<br />\n昨夜(21)晚上十一時，防暴警員進入元朗賽馬會廣場，並不斷向在場記者挑釁。有指揮官走到防暴前面，大聲訓示，要求警員「不得超越封鎖線」，並保持border line，及唔好和記者有接觸(contact)。<br />\n<br />\n惟該指揮官退下後，後方馬上舉起黑橙二旗，未幾防暴更失控，向在場記者狂噴胡椒。<br />\n<br />\n片段清楚見到，前線警員完全不受控制，即使上司有指令訓示，亦當耳邊風我行我素，警員服從能力可見一斑。<br />\n<br />\n叫曬唔可以過border line <br />\n一行返去後面班狗就當佢無到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇下最尾個指揮狗個樣尷撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"400b4fe761559140a75f8b4155cc718c19cf0102","tid":1833301,"uid":5416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T21:06:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ee9b935d924bccbd276773d471403a84781abb79","tid":1833301,"uid":5416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T21:08:15.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"9e809e2ee687ed197f26da7f2d0f291263183cb1","tid":1833301,"uid":5416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T21:10:16.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"0d75a3aafbc484e555b234ec4261acfd889600ba","tid":1833301,"uid":5416,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T21:11:33.000Z","msg":"推4"},{"pid":"6